name: Geekbench: Navigation
description: Generates 24 different routes between a sequence of locations on two OpenStreetMap maps (one for a small city, one for a large city) using Dijkstra's algorithm.The score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
